precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign an AGREEMENT for
the PROMOTION and PROTECTION OF INVESTMENTS between Canada and the LEBANESE
REPUBLIC, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing its
signature by the Hon. Arthur C. Eggleton or Ambassador Daniel Marchand.
